enn, B. H., Kolar, W. A., Howell, J. R. | title=Exergy analysis of solar powered desiccant cooling system | journal=Proc. Of the American Section of the Intern. Solar Energy Society | year=1982 | volume= | issue= | pages= 567\u2013572 | url= }}\n\n{{refend}}\n\n==Further reading==\n*{{cite journal | last1 = Bastianoni | first1 = E. | last2 = Facchini | first2 = A. | last3 = Susani | first3 = L. | last4 = Tiezzi | year = 2007 | title = Emergy as a function of exergy | url = | journal = Energy | volume = 32 | issue = 7| pages = 1158\u20131162 | doi=10.1016/j.energy.2006.08.009}}\n*Stephen Jay Kline (1999). ''The Low-Down on Entropy and Interpretive Thermodynamics'', La Ca\u00f1ada, CA: DCW Industries. {{ISBN|1928729010}}.\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=JournalURL&_cdi=5710&_auth=y&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=1f87f1e1820a1470d40891d79b39b3f6 Energy, Incorporating Exergy, An International Journal]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20050210183514/http://www.fes.uwaterloo.ca/u/jjkay/pubs/exergy/biblio.html An Annotated Bibliography of Exergy/Availability]\n*[http://exergy.se/goran/thesis/ ''Exergy \u2013 a useful concept'' by G\u00f6ran Wall]\n*[http://exergy.se/ftp/exergetics.pdf ''Exergetics'' textbook for self-study by G\u00f6ran Wall]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20050323082126/http://imartinez.etsin.upm.es/bk3/c03/Exergy.htm ''Exergy'' by Isidoro Martinez]\n*[http://www.exergoecology.com/excalc ''Exergy calculator'' by The Exergoecology Portal]\n*[https://gcep.stanford.edu/research/exergy/resourcechart.html ''Global Exergy Resource Chart'']\n*[http://www.lowex.net/english/inside/frames/text/material_in.html ''Guidebook to IEA ECBCS Annex 37, Low Exergy Systems for Heating and Cooling of Buildings'']\n*[http://www.lowex.net/english/inside/frames/text/material_in.html ''Introduction to the Concept of Exergy'']\n\n{{Industrial ecology}}\n\n[[Category:Thermodynamic free energy]]\n[[Category:State functions]]\